   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Year four of Imperator Caesar Nerva Trajanus Augustus Germanicus. Has performed for five days for work on dikes for the same fourth year in the desert canal of Polemon, (2nd h.) on behalf of Tebtunis, Horos, son of Horos, grandson of N.N. (3rd h.) for Hermodoros, son of Isidoros, son of Herakles, his mother is Tap[- -]. (4th h.) I, Isidoros, have signed. (5th h.) I, Aphrodeitos, have signed. (6th h.) I, Dionysios, have signed.</ab>
         </div>
